David G. Hirz 
Executive Compensation
As President and Chief Executive Officer at SMART & FINAL STORES INC, David G. Hirz  made $3,564,674 in total compensation.  Of this total $923,077 was received as a salary, $261,250 was received as a bonus, $1,103,207 was received in stock options, $1,249,997 was awarded as stock and $27,143 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


