Executive Profile
David G. Hirz  Chief Executive Officer, President and Director, Smart & Final Stores, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 1 Board Members in 1 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships62$3,564,674As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. David G. Hirz, also known as Dave has been the Chief Executive Officer and President of Smart & Final Stores, Inc. since January 2012 and  April 2010 respectively. Mr. Hirz served as the President and Chief Operating Officer of Smart & Final Stores, Inc. from April 2010 to January 2012. He joined Smart & Final Stores in April 2010. He served as the President of Ralphs Supermarkets at Ralphs Grocery Company from March 2004 to September 2007. He served as the President ... of Food 4 Less Division at Kroger Co., from 1999 to 2004 and from September 2007 to April 2010. He served as President of Ralph's Grocery Company Inc., a unit of Kroger Co., from September 9, 2004 to August 19, 2007. Prior to that, he served as Group Vice President, Operations of Food 4 Less. He joined Food 4 Less in 1991. Before that, Mr. Hirz held leadership positions with The Boys Markets from 1985 to 1991, including Store Director, District Manager and Manager of Store Operations and Administration. He began his supermarket industry career in 1971 as a Courtesy Clerk with Fisher-Fazio Markets in Cleveland. He has been a Director of Smart & Final Stores, Inc. since January 2012. Mr. Hirz is a graduate of California State University, Fullerton.Read Full Background




